1.title: 1. Installation
1.content: This is the base Jekyll theme. You can find out more info about customizing your Jekyll theme, as well as basic Jekyll usage documentation at jekyllrb.com . You can find the source code for Minima at GitHub: jekyll / minima . You can find the source code for Jekyll at GitHub: jekyll / jekyll .
